document.query: CREATE TABLE `delivery_method_postcode` ( `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `delivery_method_id` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `from_range` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `to_range` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `state` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci, `shipping_fee` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci, `surcharge` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci, `disable` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci, `created_at` datetime COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `updated_at` datetime COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;
